1. *Dane* su došli da vide najnovije filmove. (The days have come to see the latest movies.)
2. On je pre nekoliko *dana* proveo sa njom. (He spent some days with her a few days ago.)
3. Promenio je svoj život u poslednjih nekoliko *dana*. (He changed his life in the last few days.)
4. Ona će sutra biti na putu još nekoliko *dana*. (She will be on the road for a few more days tomorrow.)
5. Narednih *dana* ćemo raditi na projektu. (We will be working on the project in the coming days.)